@startuml variable-antes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 11
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor<<domain>> #E8F5E9
  BackgroundColor<<graph>> #FFEBEE
  BackgroundColor<<potential>> #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #333333
}

class Variable <<domain>> {
  .. Campos de dominio ..
  # name : String
  - baseName : String
  - timeSlice : int
  - states : State[]
  - variableType : VariableType
  # partitionedInterval : PartitionedInterval
  - additionalProperties : Map<String,String>
  # statesAdditionalProperties : HashMap  <<nullable>>
  - precision : double
  - unit : StringWithProperties
  - agent : StringWithProperties
  - decisionCriterion : Criterion
  __
  .. Constructores (7) ..
  + Variable(name, states)
  + Variable(name, stateNames...)
  + Variable(name, numStates)
  + Variable(variable)  // copy
  + Variable(name)  // continuous
  + Variable(name, leftClosed, min, max, rightClosed, precision)
  + Variable(name, states, partitionedInterval, precision)
  __
  .. Getters / Setters (30+) ..
  + getName() / setName()
  + getBaseName() / setBaseName()
  + getTimeSlice() / setTimeSlice()
  + isTemporal()
  + getStates() / setStates()
  + getVariableType() / setVariableType()
  + getPartitionedInterval() / setPartitionedInterval()
  + getPrecision() / setPrecision()
  + getUnit() / setUnit()
  + getAgent() / setAgent()
  + getDecisionCriterion() / setDecisionCriterion()
  + getAdditionalProperty() / setAdditionalProperty()
  + getStateAdditionalProperty() / ...
  + getNumStates()
  + getStateName()
  + getState()
  + getStateIndex() // 3 sobrecargas
  + containsState()
  + renameState(State, String)
  + chekNewStateName()  <<typo>>
  + getNewValidName()
  __
  .. Parsing temporal (fragil) ..
  - getTimeSlice(String)  <<side-effect>>
  __
  .. <color:red>Edicion de estados</color> (depende de Node) ..
  + <color:red>modifyState(Node, StateAction, int, String)</color>
  + <color:red>replaceStates(Node, State[])</color>
  - <color:red>addStateAt(Node, int, String)</color>
  - <color:red>removeStateAt(Node, int)</color>
  - <color:red>moveStateDown(Node, int)</color>
  - <color:red>moveStateUp(Node, int)</color>
  - <color:red>renameState(int, String)</color>
  - <color:red>setUniformPotential(Node)</color>
  - <color:red>resetLink(Node)</color>
  - <color:red>getNewPartitionedInterval(Node, PI)</color>
  - <color:red>setPotentialAfter...(Node, Variable, State[])</color>
  __
  .. Creacion de potenciales ..
  + deltaTablePotential(String)  <<duplicado>>
  + deltaTablePotential(State)  <<duplicado>>
  + createDeltaTablePotential(int)  <<duplicado>>
  __
  + compareTo(Variable)  <<usa hashCode>>
  + clone()
  + toString()
}

class Node <<graph>> {
  + getVariable()
  + getPotentials()
  + setPotentials()
  + getChildren()
  + getNodeType()
  + getProbNet()
}

class ProbNet <<graph>> {
  + getChildren(Node)
  + getLinks(Node)
  + getLink(Node, Node, boolean)
}

class "Link<Node>" as Link <<graph>> {
  + hasRestrictions()
  + hasRevealingConditions()
  + setRestrictionsPotential()
  + setRevealingStates()
}

class TablePotential <<potential>> {
  + values : double[]
  + reorder()
}

class UniformPotential <<potential>>

Variable .right.> Node : <color:red>depende de
Variable ..> ProbNet : <color:red>depende de
Variable ..> Link : <color:red>depende de
Variable ..> TablePotential : crea
Variable ..> UniformPotential : <color:red>crea

note bottom of Variable
  <b>986 lineas</b>
  Mezcla modelo de dominio
  con logica de edicion del grafo.
  El parsing name/baseName/timeSlice
  es fragil y tiene side-effects.
end note

@enduml
